node.text:
Hi, As some of you may or may not know @black_tom_cruise (aka Otis Perkins) was in a major car accident this past weekend. He has had surgery on his back and right eye and is recovering. The recovery process will be a lengthy one and we need your help. Please contribute to his Go-Fund-Me account to show your support and please send prayers and positive vibes his way for a speedy recovery.
He is like a brother to me and it hurts me to see him in this condition
Please share this post! He will be recovering for a long time and will need all the help he can get!

Check my bio for the link
